Package com.cafean.client.values.components

Class AbstractValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.values.components.AbstractValue
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractCBoolean, AbstractCInteger, AbstractCReal, AbstractCString, AbstractCTable
    public abstract class AbstractValue
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class for local values: parameter values which may reference an AbstractSharedValue implementation.

    Several getters for an AbstractValue method define an implicit contract: these methods return the local value when there is no shared value reference. non-null referenced object is available, that instance's value is returned. This eliminates the need for a mode flag: set the shared value foreign-key to 0 to ensure that an AbstractValue instance returns its local value.
